product.title: Aorsher Hair Curl Barrels Replacement Parts, 40mm/1.6inch Long Hair Curling Barrel Attachments for Airwrap HS01 HS05, Rose Gold
product.description:
1.6 inch Long Hair Curling Barrels Attachments for Airwrap

 * Compatible Models: Long Hair curling barrels for Airwrap HS01/HS05. Not for Hair Dryer HD01 HD02 HD03 HD04 HD08
   
   
 * Two Directions in One Barrel: Create curls in two directions--clockwise and counterclockwise. You can design the double-sided in different curly directions as needed.
   
   
 * High Quality: Made of high quality materials for durability, withstand high temperature without deformation, can be used safely.
   
   
 * Easy to Use: The curling barrel is easy to install and use. It is recommended that the curling process time be 10 seconds, and the cold air should be used for shaping for 5 seconds.
   
   
 * Hair curling tong automatic winding of hair, with air modeling and 40mm/1.6in barrel to create voluminous curls.

Size: 18.8cm length, 40mm/1.2inch diameter.
Color: Rose Red.
Note:
1. The actual color of the item may vary slightly from the pictures shown on the website. This can be caused by many factors such as brightness of your monitor and lighting brightness.
2. Please allow slight manual measurement deviation for the data.

The product is a hair dryer accessory, the hair dryer is not included.
